Package com.src.model

Class Product

java.lang.Object
com.src.model.Product
Direct Known Subclasses:
Sale
@Entity
public class Product
extends java.lang.Object
Author:
Mihnea This class models the Product entity. We consider the Product to have a name and a price. A particular Product can only appear in one given Store, since it holds data unique to that Store(i.e. the price of the Product, which varies across Stores). The Product can also appear on Orders, and we will also persist this information regarding where and when the Products were sold, in the shape of a relationship with the Order entity. Same applies for the Sale entity, which will extend this class.
